{"type":"message","id":"26ad412d","parentId":"6f1e0772","timestamp":"2026-03-24T17:26:35.846Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_9vxw20l17omn_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 4870\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=2845\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] a\r\n[mutation proposed] a\r\n[master f9b1340] pulse: 2026-03-24 132616\n 6 files changed, 331 insertions(+), 67 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 132616.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 132616.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 132515.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 132616 - The CFI Compression Experiment identified that \"constant format\" tokens (freq=160, CFI=1.0) are metaprogramming artifacts with zero information content. The solution is a hybrid scoring function, but it hasn't been implemented and tested yet.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"mellow-gulf","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 4870\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=2845\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] a\r\n[mutation proposed] a\r\n[master f9b1340] pulse: 2026-03-24 132616\n 6 files changed, 331 insertions(+), 67 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 132616.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 132616.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 132515.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 132616 - The CFI Compression Experiment identified that \"constant format\" tokens (freq=160, CFI=1.0) are metaprogramming artifacts with zero information content. The solution is a hybrid scoring function, but it hasn't been implemented and tested yet.\r\n","name":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774373195842}}
